name: Pacsafe RFID Safe TEC Bifold Wallet
description: Low-profile design and undercover tech converge in this bifold wallet with RFID-safe fabric that shields your card chips and keeps your info safe.Made of smooth, seamless heat-welded polyurethane that is lightweight and slim.RFID-safe fabric shields your chipped ID and credit cards from scanners.6 easy-access card slots, a note slot and room for up to 13 cards.
